pardes ( english : foreign land ) is a 1997 indian hindi-language musical drama film directed by subhash ghai . it was released on 8 august 1997 . the film stars shahrukh khan , amrish puri , alok nath , and newcomers mahima chaudhry and apurva agnihotri . the film was a commercial , critical and musical hit . mahima chaudary won the best newcomer award for her performance . the film was remade in telugu as pelli kanuka ( 1998 ) .